official_title: Patient-centered Educational Material to Improve Colposcopy Adherence
inclusion_criteria:
* Age 21 years or older
* Abnormal cervical screen confirmed by cytology or pathology
* Referred to Washington University School of Medicine (WUSM) colposcopy clinic
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must be FEMALE
Must have minimum age of 21 Years
exclusion_criteria:
* History of cervical cancer
* Unable to consent
